2026-06-04 13:47:22,760 | DEBUG    |   Yes.
2026-06-04 13:47:22,760 | DEBUG    |   
2026-06-04 13:47:22,760 | DEBUG    |   Steps:
2026-06-04 13:47:22,760 | DEBUG    |   1. Render any payload containing a non-BMP character via `c.AsciiJSON(...)` (or `render.AsciiJSON`).
