2026-06-04 13:47:51,601 | DEBUG    |   
2026-06-04 13:47:51,601 | DEBUG    |   1. **Regression (issue repro):** payload `{"msg": "😀"}` (U+1F600) — assert body matches expected escaped form with `\ud83d\ude00`, not `\u1f600`.
2026-06-04 13:47:51,601 | DEBUG    |   2. **Round-trip:** `json.Unmarshal` the rendered body into a `map[string]string` and `assert.Equal` on `msg` to the original emoji (catches silent corruption).
