2026-06-04 13:50:15,825 | DEBUG    |   - Emoji payload `{"msg":"😀"}` asserts escaped body is `{"msg":"\ud83d\ude00"}` (not `\u1f600`) and unmarshals back to `😀`.
2026-06-04 13:50:15,825 | DEBUG    |   - U+FFFF asserts `{"c":"\uffff"}`; U+10000 asserts `{"c":"\ud800\udc00"}` with successful unmarshal round-trip.
